OL,3,COfwat to put Thames Water in
OL,4,C'turnaround regime' and rejects 44%
OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,FRegulators have said they will impose
OL,8,Fa "turnaround oversight regime" on
OL,9,FThames Water and opposed the utility
OL,10,Ffirm's planned 44% rise in consumer
OL,11,Fbills over the next five years.
OL,13,FIn a draft verdict on England and
OL,14,FWales' water company business plans to
OL,15,F2030, Ofwat instead proposed Thames
OL,16,Fincrease average yearly bills by 23%
OL,17,Fto #535 over the period.
