OL,3,COfwat to put Thames Water in
OL,4,C'turnaround regime' and rejects 44%
OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,FThe heavily indebted Thames, which has
OL,8,F16 million customers across London and
OL,9,Fthe Thames Valley, will have to "fully
OL,10,Fre-evaluate" its current turnaround
OL,11,Fstrategy under Ofwat's measures.
OL,13,FIt will be made to publish a separate
OL,14,F"financial resilience plan", while
OL,15,FOfwat is also considering appointing a
OL,16,Fso-called independent monitor to
OL,17,Freport on the company's progress.
OL,19,FThe independent monitor would have
OL,20,F"full access" to the company's
OL,21,Ffinancial information, Ofwat said.
