OL,4,C'turnaround regime' and rejects 44%
OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,FThames will also have to provide a
OL,8,F"delivery action plan", outlining how
OL,9,Fit intends to improve its performance
OL,10,Fon sewage spills and leakage, which
OL,11,Fhas been among the worst in the
OL,12,Findustry in recent years.
OL,14,FThe watchdog also reduced Thames'
OL,15,Fplanned investment in its services,
OL,16,Fincluding upgrading its ageing
OL,17,Finfrastructure, to #16.9 billion, down
OL,18,Ffrom the #21.4 billion the company had
OL,19,Fproposed.
