OL,7,FA spokesperson for Thames Water said:
OL,8,F"Ofwat's draft determination
OL,9,Funderstandably challenges us on
OL,10,Fefficiency and delivery."
OL,12,F"They have been thoughtful in
OL,13,Fconsidering the funding we need for
OL,14,Four day-to-day running costs and the
OL,15,Fimprovements our customers and
OL,16,Fcommunities want to see."
