OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,FThe spokesperson added: "We are, in
OL,8,Fany case, taking stock of our
OL,9,Fturnaround plan under our new
OL,10,Fleadership and reflecting on our
OL,11,Fprogress to date."
OL,13,F"We will consider all of Ofwat's
OL,14,Fproposals as we go through this
OL,15,Fprocess."
OL,17,FThames is in the grips of a funding
OL,18,Fcrisis and has more than #15 billion
OL,19,Fof debt. It said this week that it
OL,20,Fonly has enough money to continue
OL,21,Ftrading until the end of May 2025.
