OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,FBosses are scrambling to secure a
OL,8,Fmajor cash injection to keep it
OL,9,Fafloat, and have held talks with both
OL,10,Fexisting shareholders and outside
OL,11,Finvestors.
OL,13,FBut chief executive Chris Weston said
OL,14,Fon Tuesday that the investment is
OL,15,F"dependent on (Thames) securing a
OL,16,Ffinal regulatory determination that is
OL,17,F... investable".
