OL,3,COfwat to put Thames Water in
OL,4,C'turnaround regime' and rejects 44%
OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,FIf Thames does not succeed in getting
OL,8,Fthe funding, it faces the prospect of
OL,9,Fbeing temporarily nationalised by the
OL,10,FGovernment and being placed in a form
OL,11,Fof special administration, meaning the
OL,12,Ftaxpayer would take on the costs of
OL,13,Fthe heavily loss-making water giant.
OL,15,FOfwat's ruling on Thursday is a draft
OL,16,Fdecision and kicks off a lengthy
OL,17,Fperiod of negotiation until its final
OL,18,Fverdict in December.
