OL,4,C'turnaround regime' and rejects 44%
OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,FHowever, the regulator has rarely made
OL,8,Fmajor deviations between its draft and
OL,9,Ffinal rulings in previous years,
OL,10,Fmeaning Thursday's statement gives
OL,11,Fcompanies an indication of how lenient
OL,12,Fit is likely to be later on.
OL,14,FIt comes as household water bills in
OL,15,FEngland and Wales are to rise by an
OL,16,Faverage #19 a year over the next five
OL,17,Fyears ` a third less than the increase
OL,18,Frequested by companies, under the
OL,19,Fdraft proposals.
