OL,3,COfwat to put Thames Water in
OL,4,C'turnaround regime' and rejects 44%
OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed will
OL,8,Fbe meeting representatives from all 16
OL,9,Fwater companies from across England
OL,10,Fand Wales on Thursday following the
OL,11,FOfwat publication.
OL,13,FOn Thursday morning, Mr Reed said he
OL,14,Fhas written to Ofwat to ask them to
OL,15,Fmake sure funding for vital
OL,16,Finfrastructure investment is ring
OL,17,Ffenced and can only be spent on
OL,18,Fupgrades benefiting customers and the
OL,19,Fenvironment.
