OL,3,COfwat to put Thames Water in
OL,4,C'turnaround regime' and rejects 44%
OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,FHe also announced that consumers will
OL,8,Fgain "new powers to hold water company
OL,9,Fbosses to account" through so-called
OL,10,Fcustomer panels.
OL,12,FHe said: "This unacceptable
OL,13,Fdestruction of our waterways should
OL,14,Fnever have been allowed, but change
OL,15,Fhas now begun so it can never happen
OL,16,Fagain."
OL,18,FOfwat chief executive David Black
OL,19,Fsaid: "Customers want to see radical
OL,20,Fchange in the way water companies care
OL,21,Ffor the environment.
