OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,F"Our draft decisions on company plans
OL,8,Fapprove a tripling of investment to
OL,9,Fmake sustained improvement to customer
OL,10,Fservice and the environment at a fair
OL,11,Fprice for customers.
OL,13,F"These proposals aim to deliver a 44%
OL,14,Freduction in spills from storm
OL,15,Foverflows compared to levels in 2021.
OL,16,FWe expect all companies to embrace
OL,17,Finnovation and go further and faster
OL,18,Fto reduce spills wherever possible.
