OL,3,COfwat to put Thames Water in
OL,4,C'turnaround regime' and rejects 44%
OL,5,Cbills hike plan
OL,7,F"Today's announcement also increases
OL,8,Fthe resilience of our water supplies
OL,9,Fto the impact of climate change and
OL,10,Fwill reduce how much water is taken
OL,11,Ffrom rivers by enabling a range of
OL,12,Flong-term water supply projects, which
OL,13,Fincludes plans for 9 reservoirs.
OL,15,F"Let me be very clear to water
OL,16,Fcompanies ` we will be closely
OL,17,Fscrutinising the delivery of their
OL,18,Fplans and will hold them to account to
OL,19,Fdeliver real improvements to the
OL,20,Fenvironment and for customers and on
OL,21,Ftheir investment programmes."
